_sText:
Don't forget to rate and comment !

A simple aim map with one level.

You can break all the 64*64 boxes (250 hp), you can also break the doors (10 hp).

There is two teleports, the right one will teleport you at the same side, and the left one at the other side. 

I'm sorry, but there is NO easter egg on this map :)

That's all, enjoy !
